commit.message: Reduce the use of Char8 module
test-large-files: generate less files to fit into GHA limits
Writing entries: go from PosixString to ByteString directly, not through String and BS.pack
Test serialising entries with Unicode filenames
Decomission the last use case of packAscii
Support Unicode in long file names
Bump GHC to 9.2.8 in CI CentOS job
Add CI job to test memory consumption on large files
